body: It's true that there's no `_convolution-2-...`, but there is a `_convolution-3-...` op. I just traced ResNet18 and it's also using `aten::_convolution`, but one of the inputs (bias) is always coming from the `Undefined` nodes, and it really has 3 inputs.
